---
title: Cal Smart Hoisin-Ginger Double Turkey with Savoury Rice and Stir-Fried Veggies
description: This classic Southeast Asian-inspired combo of tender poultry, savoury rice and spicy sauce is full of flavour but surprisingly light. Don't forget to drizzle sauce over every bite.

